name: The AntiPixel
description: The color inversion of The Pixel by Pak.   ---   The Pixel is HSB 0-0-50, or RGB 128-128-128, or HEX #808080, size 90 bytes. The Inverted Pixel is HSB 0-0-50, or RGB 127-127-127, or HEX #7f7f7f, size 89 bytes.   ---   Are these two pixels equal?   ---   Edition of 1. 12 April 2021. @horomox
